subsection.def:
application
                    (申請) means application for a legal aid
                certificate;

Director
                    (署長) includes any public officer acting under
                the authority of regulation 3(2);

income
                    (收入) means income as determined or to be
                determined by the Director and includes benefits and privileges;

paragraph.content:
the amount of any moneys paid to him from the assistance fund established
                    under section 3 of the Traffic Accident Victims (Assistance Fund)
                    Ordinance (Cap. 229);

except as otherwise provided in subparagraph (b), if the claim is
                        settled before the date of commencement of the trial, the rate of
                        contribution is 6%;

except as otherwise provided in subparagraph (b), if the claim is
                        settled before the date of commencement of the trial, the rate of
                        contribution is 15%;

except as otherwise provided in subparagraph (b), if the claim is
                        settled before the date of commencement of the hearing of the appeal in the
                        Court of First Instance, the rate of contribution is 6%;
